{"tid":692202,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【有媽的孩子真好】慈母買二千萬樓幫廿歲仔上車 「畀首期幫手供」","createTime":"2018-06-06T12:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T17:27:07.000Z","uid":68476,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"57f81826bc40c613d998c0b29fdc6238e7c01160","tid":692202,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:16:10.000Z","msg":"【有媽的孩子真好】慈母買二千萬樓幫廿歲仔上車 「畀首期幫手供」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180606/large/1528262381_ca87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180606%2Flarge%2F1528262381_ca87.jpg&h=bb355ad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新世界旗下北角柏蔚山今日首輪開售247伙，是次入場費達2,000萬元，中午12點半為散客報到時段，位於荃灣愉景新城的售樓處出現約200名準買家出席，到場準買家以中年人士為主。<br />\n<br />\n準買家曾太居住沙田，是次打算斥資2,000萬元購入一個3房單位，予20歲出頭、仍就讀大學的阿仔上車。更表示，除了會畀首期外，更會幫手供樓，如果將來有能力就「佢自己供返」。對於近期多個新盤應市，表示自己喜歡該盤位置，價錢亦合理，亦為第一次抽新盤。"},{"pid":"15d8efabc6adfabc50a374839f6b2b0d0210a3c3","tid":692202,"uid":68375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:17:59.000Z","msg":"媽！係我呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1310052ce82b7357384f0496fc68d968dcbd1307","tid":692202,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:24:02.000Z","msg":"超on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b10ce13ac70ebb6759ad06b9c27d55d701cd62e4","tid":692202,"uid":121182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"世上只有媽媽好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29d8990b61f4603021cc76622da9e90656e657b","tid":692202,"uid":186388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:27:36.000Z","msg":"害子女。你估你個仔供到？"},{"pid":"49bd6b146a1952f74483691177221a86cf96c702","tid":692202,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:27:40.000Z","msg":"媽，我先係你個仔阿"},{"pid":"10cb2fdfab519a63cb2f9124535ff5168687965c","tid":692202,"uid":156542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:29:18.000Z","msg":"媽媽 點解唔要我？"},{"pid":"b9dcec9be5af961131407e1ea0e8635184960ce5","tid":692202,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:30:38.000Z","msg":"擺明係用個首置避稅<br />\n第日個仔真係上車點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   用老婆個個?"},{"pid":"c5d12ffd0c5949a98208302128b436a5c543cc20","tid":692202,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T12:32:48.000Z","msg":"對於近期多個新盤應市，表示自己喜歡該盤位置，價錢亦合理，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c6e7bff721c528326029cea4b9c61f334a4718","tid":692202,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T16:17:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87a41569f2c36aa55486febb033fbd6d8505197c","tid":692202,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T17:18:53.000Z","msg":"20歲仔未出黎社會捱騾仔已經完成左好多人半世目標 我認我葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0c2902316c031fed7a564e301c8b61cdb01ca1","tid":692202,"uid":59602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T17:27:07.000Z","msg":"希望佢阿仔唔好揾個閪女人做老婆，食返奶奶轉頭，R撚埋層歌"}]}